            <div class="container">
                <div class="articleTitle">Peningkatan Keterampilan: Kunci Keberhasilan</div>
                <div class="articleTxt">
                    <p>Selain kestabilan, keterampilan juga menjadi tantangan utama.</p>
                    <p>Sebanyak <strong>72 persen kaum muda merasa perlu meningkatkan pengetahuan mereka mengenai
                            lingkungan dan
                            keberlanjutan,</strong> sedangkan lainnya menginginkan penguatan keterampilan teknis serta
                        pemahaman
                        kebijakan pemerintah terkait isu ini.</p>
                    <div class="emot">
                        <ul class="emotList">
                            <li class="emotItem">
                                <div class="emotTxt">Sangat Paham</div>
                                <div class="emotWrap">
                                    <div class="emotPercent articleImg--percent">
                                        <span class="counter" data-target="12">12</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="emotImg">
                                        <img src="./asset/images/emot-5.png" alt="" loading="lazy" width="" height="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="emotItem">
                                <div class="emotTxt">Cukup Paham</div>
                                <div class="emotWrap">
                                    <div class="emotPercent articleImg--percent">
                                        <span class="counter" data-target="36">36</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="emotImg">
                                        <img src="./asset/images/emot-4.png" alt="" loading="lazy" width="" height="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="emotItem">
                                <div class="emotTxt">Ragu-ragu</div>
                                <div class="emotWrap --orange">
                                    <div class="emotPercent articleImg--percent">
                                        <span class="counter" data-target="26">26</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="emotImg">
                                        <img src="./asset/images/emot-3.png" alt="" loading="lazy" width="" height="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="emotItem">
                                <div class="emotTxt">Kurang Paham</div>
                                <div class="emotWrap --red">
                                    <div class="emotPercent articleImg--percent">
                                        <span class="counter" data-target="21">21</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="emotImg">
                                        <img src="./asset/images/emot-2.png" alt="" loading="lazy" width="" height="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="emotItem">
                                <div class="emotTxt">Tidak Paham Sama Sekali</div>
                                <div class="emotWrap --red">
                                    <div class="emotPercent articleImg--percent">
                                        <span class="counter" data-target="5">5</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="emotImg">
                                        <img src="./asset/images/emot-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" width="" height="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
